 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ECentrix Software provides companies with the information they need to make better decisions about their IT, based on knowing what IT assets a company has in place, how they are being used, and how they could be utilized more efficiently. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ECentrix Software is focused on creating solutions that help organizations extract more value from their IT, liberating them from rigid technology infrastructures and enabling them to reap the benefits of developments in Web, virtualizatino and cloud technologies. The company\u0026#8217;s products bridge the gap between existing static IT asset management tools and wider application delivery platforms, from traditional physical machines and virtual servers through to web-enabled applications and the cloud.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EBased on its Centrix WorkSpace product suite, Centrix Software helps organizations improve strategic technology decision-making, make the introduction of new technologies, such as virtualization, easier and accelerate the adoption of business-critical services by end-users. Companies can modernize their IT infrastructure within a framework that aligns with existing IT governance and security models and that is designed to mitigate the risk associated with new technology introductions.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EPrivately held, Centrix Software is headquartered in Berkshire, UK and its solutions are available through a network of value-added partners and resellers.\u003C/p\u003E",
